---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Research Workflow Guidebook
description: Choose a language and follow a research workflow guide from local setup to writing and GitHub collaboration.
lang: en
langSwitch:
  url: /ko/
  label: 한국어
pageClass: page-landing
---
{% set currentUpdates = updates.completedByLang.en %}
<main>
  <section class="landing-hero">
    <h1 class="wrap hero-h1">Efficient Research Workflow</h1>
    <p class="wrap lead">Build an efficient research workspace with LaTeX, VS Code, and GitHub</p>
    <div class="wrap hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-copy-block">
        <p class="hero-copy">
          This guidebook is for researchers working with LaTeX, VS Code, Git, and GitHub.
          Start from the language you use most, move through local setup, and continue into
          steady writing and repository collaboration.
        </p>
        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button button-primary" href="/">English</a>
          <a class="button button-secondary" href="/ko/">한국어</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="hero-panel panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">{{ ui.en.recentUpdates }}</p>
        {% if updates.currentBuild %}
          <h2 class="hero-panel-title">{{ updates.currentBuild.title }}</h2>
        {% endif %}
        <dl class="updates-list">
          {% for item in currentUpdates %}
            {% if loop.index <= 1 %}
              <div>
                <dt>{{ item.date }}</dt>
                <dd>
                  {% if item.url %}
                    <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.title }}</a>
                  {% else %}
                    {{ item.title }}
                  {% endif %}
                </dd>
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </dl>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="editorial-band">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>Route Map</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        {% for section in navigation.sections %}
          <a class="feature-card panel card--{{ section.key }}" href="{{ section.url.en }}">
            <div class="card-logo-row">
              {% if section.key == "initial-setup" %}
                <img class="card-logo" src="/assets/images/LaTeX_project_logo_bird.svg.png" alt="LaTeX">
                <img class="card-logo" src="/assets/images/Visual_Studio_Code_1.35_icon.svg.png" alt="VS Code">
              {% elif section.key == "writing-in-vs-code" %}
                <img class="card-logo" src="/assets/images/Visual_Studio_Code_1.35_icon.svg.png" alt="VS Code">
              {% elif section.key == "git-github" %}
                <img class="card-logo" src="/assets/images/Visual_Studio_Code_1.35_icon.svg.png" alt="VS Code">
                <img class="card-logo" src="/assets/images/GitHub-Mark.png" alt="GitHub">
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <p class="card-kicker">{{ section.kicker.en }}</p>
            <h3>{{ section.title.en }}</h3>
            <p>{{ section.summary.en }}</p>
          </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
